{"tid":872084,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"admin/連巴入一入,關於留言正負評既 額外 改進建議","createTime":"2018-10-22T12:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T14:30:18.000Z","uid":138409,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"86bbcf342e89e815381b60e56ee92c8ddfab552a","tid":872084,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:18:14.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打提出就係「除左果個post既樓主，其他巴絲喺比正負評之前唔好顯示個正負評結果出黎，要比完先好顯示」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/805670/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/805670/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我提議加多一樣<br />\n樓主有權選擇deactivate 正負評功能<br />\n如果熄咗個功能的話<br />\n咁就所有comment（包括樓主自己嘅#1）都無得正負評<br />\n<br />\n咁樣應該更加有助討論<br />\n因為如果唔同意樓主意見的話<br />\n就唔可以僅僅留下負評<br />\n而係要解釋（最低限度要留言）"},{"pid":"0db2e5c83a6060574143dad4bce5d06180f065e2","tid":872084,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"樓下麵包鋪冇哂雞尾包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48e029a4538ffb7126c1727eb07d571328b643e","tid":872084,"uid":1139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40f8a5a7615433b92918ba8e33e90b6da4cb62ae","tid":872084,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"都唔錯<br />\n不過依家admin連我最初步果個想法都唔係好理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主呢個仲要加多步 會改既難度又大左<br />\n不過我都覺得你想法幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacbca2f379db2b1f9c1c05f37377af22918986a","tid":872084,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f8a5a7615433b92918ba8e33e90b6da4cb62ae","tid":872084,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:43:40.000Z","msg":"都唔錯<br />\n不過依家admin連我最初步果個想法都唔係好理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 